@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : updateAircraftStatus(registrationNumber, newStatus)
activate System

note right of System: The system validates the input,\nfinds the corresponding aircraft,\nand updates its operational status.

System --> ATCC : informs operation success and returns updated aircraft
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml